{"tid":1130973,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好彩睇左averager 4，差啲比人劫財財色","createTime":"2019-04-29T11:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T02:41:30.000Z","uid":37796,"like":36,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8549845f54b2a1dd4e7ce8bfc13aa292df2a027c","tid":1130973,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚睇完averager 4 已經好夜<br />\n諗住反正大街都同後巷一樣冇人，就貪快行後巷<br />\n跟住有個芝麻人無端端從後跑上黎，拍我膊頭<br />\n我一轉身，佢就露出把西瓜刀<br />\n<br />\n芝麻人＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n芝：站住！别动！<br />\n我：&hellip;&hellip;（唔敢出聲）<br />\n芝：把电话、钱包拿来<br />\n我： 大佬有事慢慢講&hellip;<br />\n芝：你说什么？！快拿钱来！<br />\n我：不用急&hellip;冷静点，我现在就拿钱给你<br />\n（突然醒起岩岩係facebook睇過一個post）<br />\n我：老兄，你看过复仇者了没？<br />\n芝：我现在就是要等你拿钱给我买票<br />\n我：你想知道剧情吗？我现在就可以告诉你<br />\n芝：不要！<br />\n我（大聲叫）：在結局裡！美國隊長會－－<br />\n芝：（即刻掉底把刀，雙手掩耳掉頭走）<br />\n<br />\n我即刻鬆左口氣<br />\n多謝芝鋒bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我先保住我菊花同銀包電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a650833c3f4b917dad5063d8f07f94ce5c4827aa","tid":1130973,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a46fe37f40d2912670acca3351bf5f219cbb4f","tid":1130973,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"點解會有負皮比gifbb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7283253143d5429f7a1f35cb70c02e706cde0f9","tid":1130973,"uid":154160,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n氣氛效果可以寫得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26396881996dec939cc32500d4b01f94b868dba3","tid":1130973,"uid":37796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c7283253143d5429